caption.title: AMP genes induced by DENV infection.
caption.p: The mRNA levels of attacin (ATT) (A), cecropin A (CECA) (B), defencin C (DEFC) (C) and gambicin 1 (D) 1 day post DENV infection in the midgut. The mRNA levels of attacin (ATT) (E), cecropin A (CECA) (F), defencin C (G) and gambicin 1 (H) 1 day post DENV infection in the carcass. All experiments were repeated in triplicate. Student’s t-tests were used to determine the significance of difference in expression between treated and control groups. Data are represented as mean ± SEM. * p<0.05, ** p<0.01, *** p<0.001.
